    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1ApplicationController" kindref="compound">ApplicationController</ref> manages the application lifecycle and handles creation and initialization of <ref refid="classDali_1_1Window" kindref="compound">Window</ref> and <ref refid="classDali_1_1Adaptor" kindref="compound">Adaptor</ref>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>The controller must follow the lifecycle sequence: Initialize -&gt; Pause/Resume -&gt; Terminate </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
